Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 客倌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出…出…出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山贼 杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来尽出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无…无面鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无面鬼  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 那是我的木遁分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长 太假戏真做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 鸣人还真胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长的脸是最有害心脏健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么挖苦我嘛 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这浓雾中 也没其他啥能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有大人像你这么说鬼故事的 感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你胆小如鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不觉得那故事令人恐怖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就说个珍藏的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说每到这种时候就会出现那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:02:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了引导死者的灵魂 乌鸦作为先导出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帆柱上点亮的巨大鬼火就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓浓的大雾正是死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦相遇便会踏上前往死者国度的航程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说就是这样的浓雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 就是在这样的浓雾中现身的幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船什么的不过是古老的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛 怎么可能有那种东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来我一点都没信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可没看出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有风吹动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 要去幽灵船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 世上没有幽灵船什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是有吗 就在那里 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大和队长说的如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是艘很可疑的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据航海法 不可以对漂流船只置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧完成调查就能回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此 不如陪着浓眉老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 要坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要够坚强 管它是幽灵还是别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是先坚强点把晕船挺过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 青叶大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸可不是地板 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个忙碌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用它来开船的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这刷子真是历史悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是船长的贵重物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你明明是个小孩 却相当能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人比一个人强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过比起两人来 干活可是人越多越快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不赶紧搞定你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不太会停下跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 我叫飞石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人是忍者吗 很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标直指火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里最强大最伟大的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那船长比火影更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长不仅要强大要伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要处处温柔地为伙伴着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日 我也要成为一名船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 等…等等先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影不仅强大 伟大 温柔 为同伴着想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还相当有气度 那个…之后还有…之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是火影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩都有各自的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 教教我那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是之前用刷子锵锵敲地的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是船长教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刷子也是船长送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否也让我们加入你们的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处搜查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不过是艘普通的船只 大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是幽灵船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么幽灵船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是迷信来着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个不是人的灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帆柱上的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在船员之间被称为幸运的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是发光的静电气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静…静电气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么帆柱上的乌鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般情况下 乌鸦可不会出现在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半路休息的海鸟 被烟囱的烟给熏黑了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么幽灵船的话题就暂且告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们调查了一下这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船上除你之外 没有其他船员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的船员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种级别的船 需要相当的人数来运作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 刷子船长也没在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们曾经都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起海里会有幽灵船这种愚蠢的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还潜藏着更恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是传说的海怪 牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不仅仅是只螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同一座小岛般的巨型螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外壳坚硬无比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被那巨大的钳子抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么都会被碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且寄生于外壳之上的富士壶专吃活人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长和其他人 大家…大家被那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 忍者很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那家伙 替我给船长他们报仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 飞石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来打飞那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶大叔 带飞石回船里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便替我转告大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解救大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有将这件事转告给同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事需要两个人来做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶大叔更能冷静地传达消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得相当可靠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 那个任务就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那种怪物交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 我的目标可是当上火影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伙伴 一点都不害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 你还小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有你一个得救也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕 船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从登上这艘船起 这东西就一直伴随我左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我保管好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了不少毛的刷子正是我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能替我保管好 我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有未完成的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了信任我跟随而来的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要守护这艘船到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我这就收拾掉你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是拯救了木叶村的英雄 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去我们的船上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋 竟敢威胁我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是个怪物 你这家伙才没啥可怕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是怪物螃蟹 外壳太坚硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不仅坚硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还出人意料地敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶 我和船都摇晃不已 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧逃离这片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人正在为我们争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 请给我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用我的拿手本领一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶紧解救出大和队长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 请借我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上了 飞石做到了吗 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然轻而易举被抓 真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的外壳坚不可摧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说要瞄准柔软的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 把你的勇气借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧 怪物螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了飞石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你比我先实现愿望了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时间短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经成为不输火影的伟大船长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时没能跟大家一同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在鸣人替我为大家报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉舒坦了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别抬举我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了飞石 才能打倒怪物螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你已经成为我们的同伴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过该告别了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 没人会责怪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这强烈的责任感还真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不能成佛 所以我们都无法成佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 没什么好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是被那混蛋螃蟹夺去了身躯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是相当舒坦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 就是 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 借着气氛 大家来做例行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵完全失灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这暴风雨可真是要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样顺波逐流的话会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没事 这样前进可以返回预订航路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这样冲向雷之国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人 有什么东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集的火影疾风传是 战舰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炮击 嗯？那是什么啊
